{"tid":2167612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首宗國安法被告申請人身保護令遭拒！！","createTime":"2020-08-21T08:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T10:57:41.000Z","uid":246828,"like":7,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5df85b74c4be011d9096b80d1285d8f171517137","tid":2167612,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQKot4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQKot4e.jpg&h=002672c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n汁：i-cable"},{"pid":"dd58c0d953bf9e0d6d2dc2897f4095e54e813037","tid":2167612,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"967dac23b65eaaaf7bb262c0a0db7469c51fd480","tid":2167612,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"烈火戰車義士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123e9d649cf93c82ec312f791a816cc75204b70d","tid":2167612,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:25:31.000Z","msg":"判詞全文：<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2020/HCAL001601_2020.doc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fjudg%2Fword%2Fvetted%2Fother%2Fen%2F2020%2FHCAL001601_2020.doc&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=f2a29ec7\" target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2020/HCAL001601_2020.doc</a>"},{"pid":"e3f3d83a5ddd53e69979b70bae52636d0c477fc2","tid":2167612,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd58c0d953bf9e0d6d2dc2897f4095e54e813037","tid":2167612,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"首名被控違反《港區國安法》的男子唐英傑，申請人身保護令及第二度申請保釋，法官<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">周家明</span></span></strong>法官及<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">李運騰</span></span></strong>昨開庭先處理人身保護令，今日頒布書面裁決，拒絕人身保護令的申請。<br />\n<br />\n唐英傑被控一項「煽動他人分裂國家罪」及一項「恐怖活動罪」。他涉嫌在今年7月1日，在灣仔駕駛電單車撞傷警員，當時電單車上插著寫有「光復香港、時代革命」旗幟，他早前申請保釋被拒。"},{"pid":"a9f5944ba7057390982ea4cc0708a9fa4e59ffa1","tid":2167612,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:26:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cef7d87bcbebf9a405fed45d300e949324174a12","tid":2167612,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7250d6a16cbf26bff6b82dcb11628ae30af83e","tid":2167612,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:28:20.000Z","msg":"本案主審法官：周家明 李運騰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D1B985j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD1B985j.jpg&h=06925f4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周家明資深大律師於一九六四年在香港出生。一九八六年及一九八七年在香港大學分別取得法學士學位及法學專業證書。一九八七年在香港獲大律師資格，並於一九九五年在新加坡最高法院獲訟辯人及律師的資格。他於二○○四年獲委任為資深大律師。二○○九年期間曾出任高等法院原訟法庭暫委法官，並自二○一○年起出任高等法院原訟法庭特委法官，現時私人執業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C3d4XY2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC3d4XY2.jpg&h=d2e8ed6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李運騰法官於一九六六年在香港出生。一九八九年及一九九一年在香港大學分別取得法學士學位及法學專業證書。一九九三年在香港獲律師資格，二○○○年在香港獲大律師資格。一九九三年加入前律政署出任檢察官，一九九五年晉升為高級檢察官，二○○五年晉升為副首席政府律師，並於同年出任高級助理刑事檢控專員職位。他於二○一三年獲委任為區域法院法官。"},{"pid":"782c5405eafbd98adf5d806f8ca7125f048e4434","tid":2167612,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:29:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d79d2836ed3c38383f1d2479c3dcd0b819f10af","tid":2167612,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote