高層<br />\n官拜高級助理刑事檢控專員<br />\n唔走係有機會升到刑事檢控專員梁卓然個位指揮迫害</span><br />\n<br />\n1 香港大量法官係暫委法官,姐係私人市場合約制唔保證續期,要續就迫害異見人士<br />\n<br />\n2 mag court係香港初級刑事法庭,通常做親都係半路轉去法律界的人, 成績又差又老, 撈到上主任裁判官咬福利就係呢班人終生志向<br />\n<br />\n3大量警親同律政的前高層滲透法院做法官,姐係鬼國公檢法合一"},{"pid":"1a60c20515edd2911d8862873280ce6a3c816bd0","tid":2167612,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:30:48.000Z","msg":"紅官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffc0b7843c06a404c0a4314dcdc7c56b8bc0e1a","tid":2167612,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"123e9d649cf93c82ec312f791a816cc75204b70d","tid":2167612,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:25:31.000Z","msg":"判詞全文：<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2020/HCAL001601_2020.doc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fjudg%2Fword%2Fvetted%2Fother%2Fen%2F2020%2FHCAL001601_2020.doc&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=f2a29ec7\" target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2020/HCAL001601_2020.doc</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:32:57.000Z","msg":"真係笑死人 判詞全英文 但條國安法到依家都未有官方英文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f7bdd8cf2aa1b0c613c10c44134793210dcff2","tid":2167612,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:33:23.000Z","msg":"指定官都知道咩事啦"},{"pid":"b35b5172f9f98be05f98a2dbc78a5b1fd87d8797","tid":2167612,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:33:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9ba37164da27142c511a00c80f46e3763b62900","tid":2167612,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"李運騰當時撈的高級助理刑事檢控專員<br />\n<strong>再升一級就可以玩doj 的特首跑馬仔</strong>, 搶做刑事檢控專員<br />\n<br />\n刑事檢控專員 梁卓然就係實際上doj最大的人<br />\n因為直接幫中共做order<br />\n<br />\n<strong>誣告遭強姦/警魔打成傷殘的示威者就係梁卓然做總指揮官</strong><br />\n公民黨同大律師公會一定知而扮傻唔出聲"},{"pid":"304ab79a92a10d541fbafd7f58d9b80211e4ce51","tid":2167612,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:48:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b65379edd4bf3c78a23cf6138bb06ca77601ac63","tid":2167612,"uid":123774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHs5Hqf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHs5Hqf.jpg&h=afa41d66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b42d8d12a9d20c08f3a8124bd9b4e471d5da415","tid":2167612,"uid":221666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:48:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3706aea0de47f4a1beffebf8c79687d13c7497d","tid":2167612,"uid":12186,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:50:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31dae45026926e41ed9d7f4a181e65092e7e73f5","tid":2167612,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:50:30.000Z","msg":"即係未審先坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb259dbf96e9acbda2fe0cdafcd8d4ee6b9e23a1","tid":2167612,"uid":289214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d79d2836ed3c38383f1d2479c3dcd0b819f10af","tid":2167612,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e3f3d83a5ddd53e69979b70bae52636d0c477fc2","tid":2167612,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd58c0d953bf9e0d6d2dc2897f4095e54e813037","tid":2167612,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"首名被控違反《港區國安法》的男子唐英傑，申請人身保護令及第二度申請保釋，法官<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">周家明</span></span></strong>法官及<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">李運騰</span></span></strong>昨開庭先處理人身保護令，今日頒布書面裁決，拒絕人身保護令的申請。<br />\n<br />\n唐英傑被控一項「煽動他人分裂國家罪」及一項「恐怖活動罪」。他涉嫌在今年7月1日，在灣仔駕駛電單車撞傷警員，當時電單車上插著寫有「光復香港、時代革命」旗幟，他早前申請保釋被拒。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"渣電單車車到人&gt;交通意外<br />\n渣電單車撞到狗&gt;襲警<br />\n渣電單車插住枝旗撞到狗&gt;煽動他人分裂國家+罪恐怖活動罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"揸的士沖入人群，撞斷人對腳，徹控，收幾十萬"},{"pid":"e16c01540387fc3983a7fbde5e4be4ef90278387","tid":2167612,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"82ef720eac62e47b14a0847c4fa6a818ef17814f","tid":2167612,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T09:15:27.000Z","msg":"我briefly睇咗判詞<br />\n特別留意以下幾點 大家評論可以針對呢幾點<br />\n<br />\n- 法庭認為國安法42條指「除非法官有充足理由相信其不會繼續實施危害國家安全行為，不得准予保釋」係類似本身法庭因爲相信被告有機會保釋期間犯案所以拒絕保釋嘅情況，並非假定不應給予保釋，無侵犯被告權利 （判詞29-30段）<br />\n<br />\n- 申請方指國安法42條「繼續」此字眼具有逼被告認罪之嫌，因為只要被告承認有危害國家安全才可以「繼續」危害國家安全，法庭拒絕接納申請方論點 （判詞30段）<br />\n<br />\n- 法庭認為國安法42條並無侵犯被告應有保釋權利，裁定符合基本法及公民與政治權利國際公約 （判詞48段）<br />\n<br />\n- 法庭認為由特首指定國安法法官並無損害獨立司法權，認為特首並非指定某位特定法官審理某件特定案件，只是指定一定數量法官審理國安法案件，決定由哪位法官審理哪件案件權力仍然全屬司法機關，不接納政府能干預司法機關審理國安法的司法權　（判詞54-55段）"}}